{
  "stem": "2723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I am very aware of it, because my maternal grandfather was known to be one of the most brilliant men in Slovakia in law.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was also the head of the Jewish community for many, many years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was held in great esteem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there is, to my amazement, a lot of survived documentation on him, in Slovakia, at this point.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was brought up in what is probably conservative-- leaning towards the very liberal Jewish style.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never knew my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my mother talked of him a great deal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in his spirit, I suppose she tackled my Jewish education, such as it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father was not very religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He came from a much more orthodox background than my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I think he sort of gradually eased off, went along with my mother's symbols and observance, which was not, strangely enough, Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We only had all the holidays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I can remember going with my father, and my grandmother and mother, to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But Friday was not observed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I know that my mother was a very strongly conscious Jewish woman, who instilled that in me to the very end, really.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I also know that there was a possibility, more than once, to have an out by conversion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mother was violently against it, and made it quite, quite known to my sister and I, who maybe would have benefited at times from being converts, that this was not going to be an option.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I am afraid I have to correct that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was barely two years between us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were very healthy siblings who fought a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really didn't have a chance to develop a proper relationship with her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were a very, very different.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
